FIG. 3 illustratively represents a reside of the Li-ion secondary battery pack showing the output terminals according to the embodiment;


FIG. 4 is a circuit block diagram for indicating an arrangement of a recharging system for recharging the Li-ion secondary battery pack, according to an embodiment of the present invention;


FIG. 5 is a flow chart for describing a recharging control operation executed by the Li-ion battery pack recharging system of FIG. 4;


FIG. 6 is a flow chart for explaining another recharging control operation performed by the Li-ion battery pack recharging system of FIG. 4;


FIG. 7 is a time chart for representing the recharging operation by the Li-ion battery pack recharging system of FIG. 4; and


FIG. 8 is a circuit block diagram for showing the arrangement of the conventional Li-ion battery pack recharging system.
